    "text": "Game Operations\nRole ownership for planning, tracking, and post-game workflows.\nHelp - Game Operations\n← Back to Help Portal\nGame Operations\nRole ownership for planning, tracking, and post-game workflows.\nGame and Practice Planning\n- Coach/Admin: Build game/practice schedule in edit-schedule.html .\n- Coach/Admin: Add officiating slots to games, assign officials from the directory, and review coverage status in edit-schedule.html .\n- Coach/Admin: Prepare game plans in game-plan.html .\n- Coach/Admin: Prepare drills in drills.html .\nOfficiating Assignments\n- Coach/Admin: Add officiating slots and enable per-game self-assignment in edit-schedule.html .\n- Official: Review assigned games, accept or decline, mark can't make it, submit final score and notes after the game, and claim open slots in officials.html . Open slot self-assignment is restricted to eligible team participants (team owner, admin, parent, roster member, or global admin).\n- Coach/Admin: Assignment response and coverage status are visible on the schedule editor game card.\nTracking Workflows\n- Coach/Admin: Standard tracker in track.html .\n- Coach/Admin: Live tracker in track-live.html .\n- Coach/Admin: Basketball live tracker in live-tracker.html .\n- Coach/Admin: Basketball beta tracker in track-basketball.html .\n- Coach/Admin: Statsheet tracking in track-statsheet.html .\n- Volunteer (Stream & Score): Combined scorekeeper + streaming access in a single game-day workspace. Routed from game-day entry when the Stream & Score access level is granted.\nGame Day and Reports\n- Coach/Admin: Game day operation in game-day.html .\n- Parent/Coach/Admin/Member: Game report viewing in game.html .\n- Parent/Coach/Admin: Player-centric report drilldown in player.html ."
